#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn12.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.23:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Dasabalavagga "
msgstr "3. The Ten Powers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Upanisasutta "
msgstr "23. Vital Conditions "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn12.23:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.23:1.2"
msgid "“Jānato ahaṃ, bhikkhave, passato āsavānaṃ khayaṃ vadāmi, no ajānato no apassato. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I say that the ending of defilements is for one who knows and sees, not for one who does not know or see. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:1.3"
msgid "Kiñca, bhikkhave, jānato kiṃ passato āsavānaṃ khayo hoti? "
msgstr "For one who knows and sees what? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:1.4"
msgid "Iti rūpaṃ iti rūpassa samudayo iti rūpassa atthaṅgamo, "
msgstr "‘Such is form, such is the origin of form, such is the ending of form. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:1.5"
msgid "iti vedanā … pe … "
msgstr "Such is feeling … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:1.6"
msgid "iti saññā … "
msgstr "Such is perception … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:1.7"
msgid "iti saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "Such are choices … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:1.8"
msgid "iti viññāṇaṃ iti viññāṇassa samudayo iti viññāṇassa atthaṅgamoti. "
msgstr "Such is consciousness, such is the origin of consciousness, such is the ending of consciousness.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato āsavānaṃ khayo hoti. "
msgstr "The ending of the defilements is for one who knows and sees this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.30, sc2
msgctxt "sn12.23:2.1"
msgid "Yampissa taṃ, bhikkhave, khayasmiṃ khayeñāṇaṃ, tampi saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that this knowledge of ending has a vital condition, it doesn’t lack a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.2"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, khayeñāṇassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.3"
msgid "‘Vimuttī’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Freedom.’ "

#. VAR: Vimuttimpāhaṃ → vimuttimpahaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn12.23:2.4"
msgid "Vimuttimpāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that freedom has a vital condition, it doesn’t lack a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.5"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, vimuttiyā upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.6"
msgid "‘Virāgo’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Dispassion.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.7"
msgid "Virāgampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that dispassion has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.8"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, virāgassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.9"
msgid "‘Nibbidā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Disillusionment.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.10"
msgid "Nibbidampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that disillusionment has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.11"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, nibbidāya upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.12"
msgid "‘Yathābhūtañāṇadassanan’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Truly knowing and seeing.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.13"
msgid "Yathābhūtañāṇadassanampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that truly knowing and seeing has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.14"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, yathābhūtañāṇadassanassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.15"
msgid "‘Samādhī’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Immersion.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:2.16"
msgid "Samādhimpāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that immersion has a vital condition. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn12.23:3.1"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, samādhissa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.2"
msgid "‘Sukhan’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Bliss.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.3"
msgid "Sukhampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that bliss has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.4"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, sukhassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.5"
msgid "‘Passaddhī’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Tranquility.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.6"
msgid "Passaddhimpāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that tranquility has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.7"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, passaddhiyā upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.8"
msgid "‘Pītī’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Rapture.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.9"
msgid "Pītimpāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that rapture has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.10"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, pītiyā upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.11"
msgid "‘Pāmojjan’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Joy.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.12"
msgid "Pāmojjampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that joy has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.13"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, pāmojjassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.14"
msgid "‘Saddhā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Faith.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:3.15"
msgid "Saddhampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that faith has a vital condition. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.31, sc4
msgctxt "sn12.23:4.1"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, saddhāya upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.2"
msgid "‘Dukkhan’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Suffering.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.3"
msgid "Dukkhampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that suffering has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.4"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, dukkhassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.5"
msgid "‘Jātī’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Rebirth.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.6"
msgid "Jātimpāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that rebirth has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.7"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, jātiyā upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.8"
msgid "‘Bhavo’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Continued existence.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.9"
msgid "Bhavampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that continued existence has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.10"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, bhavassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.11"
msgid "‘Upādānan’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Grasping.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.12"
msgid "Upādānampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that grasping has a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.13"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, upādānassa upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.14"
msgid "‘Taṇhā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Craving.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.23:4.15"
msgid "Taṇhampāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanisaṃ vadāmi, no anupanisaṃ. "
msgstr "I say that craving has a vital condition. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn12.23:5.1"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, taṇhāya upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is it? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.2"
msgid "‘Vedanā’tissa vacanīyaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Feeling.’ … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.3"
msgid "‘phasso’tissa vacanīyaṃ … "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Contact.’ … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.4"
msgid "‘saḷāyatanan’tissa vacanīyaṃ … "
msgstr "You should say: ‘The six sense fields.’ … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.5"
msgid "‘nāmarūpan’tissa vacanīyaṃ … "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Name and form.’ … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.6"
msgid "‘viññāṇan’tissa vacanīyaṃ … "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Consciousness.’ … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.7"
msgid "‘saṅkhārā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Choices.’ … "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.8"
msgid "Saṅkhārepāhaṃ, bhikkhave, saupanise vadāmi, no anupanise. "
msgstr "I say that choices have a vital condition, they don’t lack a vital condition. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.9"
msgid "Kā ca, bhikkhave, saṅkhārānaṃ upanisā? "
msgstr "And what is the vital condition for choices? "

msgctxt "sn12.23:5.10"
msgid "‘Avijjā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘Ignorance.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.32, sc6
msgctxt "sn12.23:6.1"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, avijjūpanisā saṅkhārā, "
msgstr "So ignorance is a vital condition for choices. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.2"
msgid "saṅkhārūpanisaṃ viññāṇaṃ, "
msgstr "Choices are a vital condition for consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.3"
msgid "viññāṇūpanisaṃ nāmarūpaṃ, "
msgstr "Consciousness is a vital condition for name and form. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.4"
msgid "nāmarūpūpanisaṃ saḷāyatanaṃ, "
msgstr "Name and form are vital conditions for the six sense fields. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.5"
msgid "saḷāyatanūpaniso phasso, "
msgstr "The six sense fields are vital conditions for contact. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.6"
msgid "phassūpanisā vedanā, "
msgstr "Contact is a vital condition for feeling. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.7"
msgid "vedanūpanisā taṇhā, "
msgstr "Feeling is a vital condition for craving. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.8"
msgid "taṇhūpanisaṃ upādānaṃ, "
msgstr "Craving is a vital condition for grasping. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.9"
msgid "upādānūpaniso bhavo, "
msgstr "Grasping is a vital condition for continued existence. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.10"
msgid "bhavūpanisā jāti, "
msgstr "Continued existence is a vital condition for rebirth. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.11"
msgid "jātūpanisaṃ dukkhaṃ, "
msgstr "Rebirth is a vital condition for suffering. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.12"
msgid "dukkhūpanisā saddhā, "
msgstr "Suffering is a vital condition for faith. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.13"
msgid "saddhūpanisaṃ pāmojjaṃ, "
msgstr "Faith is a vital condition for joy. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.14"
msgid "pāmojjūpanisā pīti, "
msgstr "Joy is a vital condition for rapture. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.15"
msgid "pītūpanisā passaddhi, "
msgstr "Rapture is a vital condition for tranquility. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.16"
msgid "passaddhūpanisaṃ sukhaṃ, "
msgstr "Tranquility is a vital condition for bliss. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.17"
msgid "sukhūpaniso samādhi, "
msgstr "Bliss is a vital condition for immersion. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.18"
msgid "samādhūpanisaṃ yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ, "
msgstr "Immersion is a vital condition for truly knowing and seeing. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.19"
msgid "yathābhūtañāṇadassanūpanisā nibbidā, "
msgstr "Truly knowing and seeing is a vital condition for disillusionment. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.20"
msgid "nibbidūpaniso virāgo, "
msgstr "Disillusionment is a vital condition for dispassion. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.21"
msgid "virāgūpanisā vimutti, "
msgstr "Dispassion is a vital condition for freedom. "

msgctxt "sn12.23:6.22"
msgid "vimuttūpanisaṃ khayeñāṇaṃ. "
msgstr "Freedom is a vital condition for the knowledge of ending. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
#. VAR: kusobbhe → kussubbhe (si, s1-3, km) | kusubbhe (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.23:7.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, uparipabbate thullaphusitake deve vassante taṃ udakaṃ yathāninnaṃ pavattamānaṃ pabbatakandarapadarasākhā paripūreti. Pabbatakandarapadarasākhāparipūrā kusobbhe paripūrenti. Kusobbhā paripūrā mahāsobbhe paripūrenti. Mahāsobbhā paripūrā kunnadiyo paripūrenti. Kunnadiyo paripūrā mahānadiyo paripūrenti. Mahānadiyo paripūrā mahāsamuddaṃ paripūrenti. "
msgstr "It’s like when it rains heavily on a mountain top, and the water flows downhill to fill the hollows, crevices, and creeks. As they become full, they fill up the pools. The pools fill up the lakes, the lakes fill up the streams, and the streams fill up the rivers. And as the rivers become full, they fill up the ocean. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn12.23:8.1"
msgid "Evameva kho, bhikkhave, avijjūpanisā saṅkhārā, saṅkhārūpanisaṃ viññāṇaṃ, viññāṇūpanisaṃ nāmarūpaṃ, nāmarūpūpanisaṃ saḷāyatanaṃ, saḷāyatanūpaniso phasso, phassūpanisā vedanā, vedanūpanisā taṇhā, taṇhūpanisaṃ upādānaṃ, upādānūpaniso bhavo, bhavūpanisā jāti, jātūpanisaṃ dukkhaṃ, dukkhūpanisā saddhā, saddhūpanisaṃ pāmojjaṃ, pāmojjūpanisā pīti, pītūpanisā passaddhi, passaddhūpanisaṃ sukhaṃ, sukhūpaniso samādhi, samādhūpanisaṃ yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ, yathābhūtañāṇadassanūpanisā nibbidā, nibbidūpaniso virāgo, virāgūpanisā vimutti, vimuttūpanisaṃ khayeñāṇan”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, ignorance is a vital condition for choices. … Freedom is a vital condition for the knowledge of ending.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.23:8.2"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

